1) Product Service
Before API Gateway:-
POST :- http://localhost:8080/api/product
GET  :- http://localhost:8080/api/product

After API Gateway:-
POST :- http://localhost:8888/api/product
GET  :- http://localhost:8888/api/product

2) Order Service
Before API Gateway:-
POST :- http://localhost:8080/api/order
After API Gateway:-
POST :- http://localhost:8888/api/order

3) Inventory Service
Before API Gateway:-
GET :- http://localhost:8080/api/inventory
After API Gateway:-
GET :- http://localhost:8888/api/inventory